Interface TxStateVisitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FulltextIndexTransactionStateVisitor, TransactionCountingStateVisitor, TransactionToRecordStateVisitor, TxStateVisitor.Adapter, TxStateVisitor.Delegator
    public interface TxStateVisitor
extends AutoCloseable
    A visitor for visiting the changes that have been made in a transaction.
